PrecisAuthority for the Right Honourable Jean Chrétien or the Minister of Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a TREATY ON MUTUAL ASSISTANCE IN CRIMINAL MATTERS between Canada and the ARGENTINE REPUBLIC, or (b) to execute an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing the Ambassador or another official to sign the Treaty on behalf of Canada.

precis:
Authority for the Right Honourable Jean Chrétien or the Minister of
Foreign Affairs (a) to sign a TREATY ON MUTUAL ASSISTANCE IN CRIMINAL
MATTERS between Canada and the ARGENTINE REPUBLIC, or (b) to execute an
Instrument of Full Powers authorizing the Ambassador or another official
to sign the Treaty on behalf of Canada.
